# Entra Connect Core Module

**Author:** Adrian Johnson (adrian207@gmail.com)  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Date:** December 2024

This module provides core Entra Connect operations and server management capabilities.

## Functions

### Install-EntraConnectServer
Installs and configures Entra Connect server.

### Configure-EntraConnectSync
Configures synchronization settings and methods.

### Get-EntraConnectHealthStatus
Retrieves Entra Connect health and sync status.

### Set-EntraConnectAuthenticationMethod
Configures authentication methods including PHS, PTA, and Federation.

### Start-EntraConnectSync
Initiates synchronization process.

### Get-EntraConnectSyncStatus
Gets current synchronization status and statistics.

### Set-EntraConnectFiltering
Configures OU and attribute filtering.

### Enable-EntraConnectSeamlessSSO
Enables seamless single sign-on.

### Configure-EntraConnectStagingMode
Configures staging mode for safe testing.

### Get-EntraConnectConfiguration
Retrieves current Entra Connect configuration.
